---
globs: engine/**,extension/**
alwaysApply: false
---

Layer boundaries: engine/dynamics = ingest-side kernels (all dense math, MKL);
engine/synthesis = output/GGUF export; engine/core = hashing/glicko2/hilbert/perfcache.
C#/SQL orchestrate only; no GPU code anywhere here (structural). New source file ⇒ add
to BOTH HEADERS and SOURCES in that target's CMakeLists.txt. After ANY engine rebuild,
run `cmd /c "scripts\win\build-extensions.cmd"` (static-lib import ⇒ extension freshness
≠ engine freshness). Confirm with `substrate_health()` / `api(...)`. rc==0 is success in
native lookups. Full rules: `.github/instructions/engine-native.instructions.md` — read it.
